{
  "name": "triple_screen_elder_v17_structural_repair",
  "description": "Elder Triple Screen v17 — structural repair over v132. Uses the repaired oscillator path, optional intermediate-timeframe oscillator, and optional trend-strength gate borrowed from the stricter v132b family. Tests whether a more canonical three-screen structure can keep the smoother short-only shape while recovering net.",
